snippet.textDisplay: Thanks to Habib for presenting 'Jadu Jaane' by Bishwanath, another pride of Sylhet Baul Khwaj Mia. He passed away a few days ago, maybe he would have liked to see this performance. But I don't know where I missed Kaya/Helal brothers in this Moha Yajna of Folk!! Krishna and Maya, even after 20/22 years, the Moha spreads among everyone, that Moha could have been spread once again through Coke Studio.... If Kaya or Helal brother was put in this song instead of a foreigner, it would have just caught fire, the fire
